Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Magsaysay Elementary School to Lamisahan Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 824
An Act Changing the Name of the Magsaysay Elementary School to Lamisahan Elementary School
Section 1. The name of the Magsaysay Elementary School in Barangay Lamisahan, City of Zamboanga, is hereby changed to Lamisahan Elementary School.1a\^/phi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 27, 1984
